articles.title: Celine Dion cancels tour dates as a result of neurological disorder - The Guardian
articles.description: The Canadian singer announced the cancellation of the European leg of her Courage World Tour as she continues to battle Stiff Person Syndrome
articles.content:
Celine Dion has cancelled all of her tour dates for 2023 and 2024 as she continues to deal with a rare neurological disorder known as Stiff Person Syndrome.
